"Institutions Should Use and Teach Free Software"
msgstr ""
"<a href=\"/education/education.html\">Obrazovanje</a> &rarr; <a href=\"/"
"education/education.html#indepth\">Detalji</a> &rarr; Zašto bi obrazovne "
